	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The difference between Everdrives and the old cheap flashcarts is massive, though. Everdrives have almost perfect compatibility, whereas the Smart Card requires a lot of patches, doesn't have a RTC, and even with patches may not work with some games.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


